  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="faq-inner">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What is AI SEO and how is it different from traditional SEO?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>

<p>AI SEO uses artificial intelligence and machine learning to automate and enhance every part of the SEO process — from keyword research and content creation to technical audits and competitor analysis. Unlike traditional SEO which relies on manual research, AI processes thousands of data points instantly, identifies patterns humans can't see, and adapts strategies in real time. The result: faster rankings, better content, and stronger ROI for Auckland small businesses.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How quickly will I see results from AI SEO in Auckland?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>

<p>Most Auckland businesses see meaningful ranking improvements within 2–4 months with AI SEO, compared to 4–6 months with traditional methods. AI accelerates the process by identifying quick-win keywords faster, publishing optimised content at scale, and automatically resolving technical issues. Some clients see early improvements for low-competition terms in as little as 6 weeks.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Is AI SEO suitable for small businesses in New Zealand?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>

<p>Absolutely — AI SEO is especially powerful for NZ small businesses because it levels the playing field against larger competitors with bigger budgets. Our AI tools allow us to deliver enterprise-grade SEO strategy at small business prices. Whether you're a local Auckland tradesperson, retailer, or professional services firm, AI SEO can consistently generate organic leads from Google.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What AI tools do you use for SEO?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>

<p>We use a combination of leading AI platforms for keyword intelligence, natural language generation for content, machine learning-based technical audit tools, and predictive analytics dashboards. All AI output is reviewed and refined by our experienced NZ SEO specialists to ensure accuracy, brand alignment, and compliance with Google's quality guidelines.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you offer a free AI SEO audit for Auckland businesses?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>

<p>Yes! We offer a complimentary AI SEO audit for all Auckland and NZ businesses. Our AI audit analyses your website's technical health, current keyword rankings, content quality, backlink profile, and competitor positions. Contact us below or call <a href="tel:+64210396580">021 039 6580</a> to book your free audit.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How much does AI SEO cost for a small business in NZ?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>

<p>Our AI SEO packages start from NZD $799/month for the Starter plan, which covers AI keyword research, on-page optimisation, Google Business Profile management, and monthly reporting. The Growth plan at $1,499/month includes full AI content creation and link building. Enterprise pricing is custom. All plans are month-to-month with no lock-in contract.</p>

<!-- ===== CTA ===== -->

Ready to Rank?</div>
      </details>
    </div>
